{"tid":1952824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第卅貳期牆紙】 權疫的遊戲","createTime":"2020-03-31T23:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T03:26:22.000Z","uid":253119,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b92734211640e003c3d8472d30720bc600db7772","tid":1952824,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情越發嚴峻，政府兒戲的防疫政策在此時迎來苦果，只能頒下禁聚令來防範社區爆發。<br />\n<br />\n我們曾期望會有一個負責任的政府，卻在看到管治班子無心無力、警察以防疫之名肆意弄權之後屢屢失望。<br />\n<br />\n今期，我們訪問了劉穎匡先生對初選及制度抗爭的看法；亦邀請了甄拔濤先生與我們談談藝術的抗爭，希望能為在家抗疫的讀者們帶來一點思考。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 素人&middot;困境  <br />\n2. 公民監察，一齊聯署  <br />\n3. 惡法非法&mdash;&mdash;反恐與公安  <br />\n4. 從鄭麗琼被捕說起&mdash;&mdash;法律正確無誤？  <br />\n5. 專訪劉穎匡  <br />\n6. 藝術的抗爭 抗爭的藝術<br />\n7. Kenji Wong&mdash;&mdash;讓我們下定決心，光復香港<br />\n8. 大時代下的紀錄 韓麗珠《黑日》<br />\n9. 保家衛園 1941-2019<br />\n10. 香港政治光譜<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#32期 #32nd<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJn1xpo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJn1xpo.jpg&h=de45b5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Soy8cpp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoy8cpp.jpg&h=6a3ea9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZLKva5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZLKva5.jpg&h=28ca802a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2C88cpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2C88cpr.jpg&h=bbcbc94c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoUbUCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoUbUCN.jpg&h=2688f280&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12wNsXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb